   "source": [
    "# Inventory Management Simulation\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook implements a fixed-cycle ordering policy simulation for inventory management.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Overview\n",
    "- **Fixed Cycle Ordering**: Order a fixed quantity every T days\n",
    "- **Deterministic Demand**: Constant daily demand based on annual demand\n",
    "- **Lead Time**: Orders can have a lead time before receipt\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Import Required Modules"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import importlib\n",
    "import inventory.inventory_models\n",
    "importlib.reload(inventory.inventory_models)\n",
    "from inventory.inventory_models import InventoryParams\n",
    "import inventory.inventory_analysis\n",
    "importlib.reload(inventory.inventory_analysis)\n",
    "from inventory.inventory_analysis import InventorySimulation\n",
    "import warnings\n",
    "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore', category=DeprecationWarning)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ All modules imported successfully\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Check Directory Structure"
